text: The 2006 O'Byrne Cup was a Gaelic football competition played by the teams of Leinster GAA. The competition differs from the Leinster Senior Football Championship as it also features further education colleges. ==O'Byrne Cup== ==O'Byrne Shield== Won by Longford, who defeated Wicklow in the final. ==References== ==External links== *Leinster G.A.A.
